data.description: If you are looking for some peace and quiet but like to be in a neighborhood, this home is perfect for you. Located in Carolina Seasons, this ranch home sits on a quiet cul-de-sac with a view of the pond across the street. Mature trees surround the property giving you privacy with no backyard neighbors. The home offers an open concept living space from the kitchen, living room to the outside screened in porch area. The back yard is great for entertaining with a large patio area and fire pit. The vaulted ceiling and skylights provide lots of natural light helping to reduce the use of electricity. All 3 bedrooms are a great size. The master bedroom has beautiful dark colored laminate flooring. The master bathroom has a large vanity, a deep jetted tub and separate shower. Don't wait to make this one yours!
